  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6a6d6a76&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FM2ibDBMdECU0lp2WFfPKX9csichwS1OwvibQHc7dpqaK8lFfdevqIy9g77D2icRYu1DY4UTlWiaRJCzRmGONXmpGdMrticQ59Dia9D0HYT5bdw9Hcg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\"><mp-common-profile class=\"custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe mp_common_widget\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"逛逛GitHub\" data-alias=\"ggGithub\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ePw3ZeGRruyXo8VzACicO8MVibibicuJUQ8Vzghx6WF8F51breYjBIuYd4cj6wp26BYrg850bNuA20rdic9UyKIUhpg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"热门「开源项目」推送到你眼前，每日为你节省 1 小时。 给我发消息可咨询各种开源项目，专注 AI、硬科技开源领域。\" data-id=\"MzUxNjg4NDEzNA==\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"0\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n  <p data-panel-group-id=\"_r_3_\" data-panel=\"\" data-panel-id=\"_r_4_\" data-panel-size=\"0.0\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">最近前端圈被一个叫 Pretext 的开源项目刷屏了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">它的作者是前 React 核心开发者，之前做过 react-motion 那个 21.9K Star 的项目。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">这次他搞了个新东西，发布&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">3 天 Star 数就超过了 react-motion。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.2\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049084\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e3ff0873&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FM2ibDBMdECU2sqicnrlYdjeqqTezcRXoMVsVvyWhKyMOQHnsh3XYl5rDBAiaWLUHvGjT7ebJebx7j7cIiacsXlYwoBibKvQCtHDAxjpDzww8q8hk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">推文 1600 万浏览、6.4 万赞，X 上相关讨论帖子超 6.8 万条。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">现在热度开始蔓延到国内了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">我花时间研究了一下，确实挺顶的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-family: Futura-Medium;font-size: 36px;font-weight: 900;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 1;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">01</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">开源项目简介</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5703703703703704\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049066\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c3f08900&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FM2ibDBMdECU3XYgOTUic8T7nFG51QkHu4Ur7ibHGDBeicICqBibDrleE7wiaQHoaLtKDUpB9x2CuPc7W0ueHph2hyV7bfYqRn2gwYOQeibGyLNicBBA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Pretext 是一个纯 JavaScript/TypeScript 的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">多行文本测量与布局库。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">说直白一点，它解决的问题是：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">在不碰 DOM 的情况下，精确算出一段文字在给定宽度下会有多高。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">先来看看效果，下面这个视频是我使用和这个库做的网页效果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">只能说，非常丝滑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;\"></p>\n  <div>\n   <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"javascript\"><code><span leaf=\"\">开源地址：<span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">https</span>:<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">//github.com/chenglou/pretext</span></span></code></pre>\n   <p></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-family: Futura-Medium;font-size: 36px;font-weight: 900;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 1;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">02</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">牛在哪里</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">多行文本灵活布局库，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">听起来好像不是什么大事。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">但这个问题在 Web 开发里</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">已经存在 30 年了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">之前想测文字高度，只能靠 getBoundingClientRect 或者 offsetHeight。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">但这些操作会强制浏览器重新计算整个页面布局，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">代价非常大。</span></span></p>\n  <mpcpc class=\"js_cpc_area res_iframe cpc_iframe\" data-category_id_list=\"5|6|17|21|41|43|48|59\" js_editor_cpcad=\"\" src=\"/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/cpc_tmpl#1775232673923\" data-id=\"1775232673923\"></mpcpc>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">在虚拟滚动列表、聊天界面、瀑布流这种需要频繁测量的场景里，性能直接拉胯。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Pretext 目前已经斩获 3.4 万+ Star，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">体积才 15KB。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">这个项目能这么火不是没原因的，几个核心设计确实有意思。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">两阶段架构，性能炸裂</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Pretext 把文本测量拆成了两步：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">第一步是 prepare(text, font)，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">负责分词、处理双向文本、用 Canvas measureText 测量每个片段的宽度并缓存。这一步相对重一些，500 段文本大概 19ms。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">第二步是 layout(prepared, maxWidth, lineHeight)，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">基于缓存的宽度做纯算术运算，算换行后的总高度。这一步极轻，500 段文本才 0.09ms。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">重点来了：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">窗口大小变化的时候，只需要重新跑第二步就行。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">prepare 的缓存还在，直接用算术就能算出新高度。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">比传统 DOM 测量快了 200 倍以上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">全语言支持，准确率 100%</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">这个库不是只测英文字母的。中文、日文、韩文啥的全都能处理。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">而且在 Chrome、Safari、Firefox 三个浏览器上的准确率都是 7680/7680，也就是 100%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">做全语言文本渲染的人都知道这有多难。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">所以一经发布，Star 数量就蹭蹭的涨。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6574074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049067\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f4a35b26&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FM2ibDBMdECU2ZwZxx8LpEOP8KyvHlNic6Xp6icLRjfIm2qbfFQ8WbE7iaXwbZzoWVaIbvT3XUzL3DMQRLTRiaWRt7Tl01YUlU8CicgBqazKjIqhibM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;