in:0px 8px 16px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">两种使用场景</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">一个是预测文本高度。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">不需要碰 DOM 就能知道文字多高，虚拟滚动列表、瀑布流布局、聊天气泡 shrink-wrap、防止布局偏移，这些场景都能用上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">二是手动逐行布局。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">可以拿到每行文字的精确坐标和内容，然后渲染到 Canvas、SVG、WebGL 上，甚至可以实现文字绕障碍物流动这种高级效果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">你最近刷到的流体烟雾 ASCII 艺术、摄像头追踪人脸做文字避让、物理球碰撞改变文字排列、Mario 游戏 ASCII 文字版，各种花活都有。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;\">这是一个 AI 辅助开发的标杆案例。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">开发者 Cheng Lou 在开发过程中大量使用了 Claude Code 和 Codex，让 AI 在几十种容器宽度下对比浏览器的真实渲染结果，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">然后自动修正差异。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Hacker News 上很多人专门聊这一点，说这是 AI 编程的完美范例。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Simon Willison 也专门写博文推荐，特别称赞了它的测试方法，用整本了不起的盖茨比做跨浏览器对比。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-family: Futura-Medium;font-size: 36px;font-weight: 900;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 1;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">04</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 16px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">部署与使用</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">安装很简单：</span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"nginx\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attribute\">npm</span>&nbsp;install&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">@chenglou</span>/pretext</span></code></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">或者用 bun：</span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"nginx\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attribute\">bun</span>&nbsp;add&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">@chenglou</span>/pretext</span></code></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">基础用法：预测文本高度</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"javascript\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">import</span>&nbsp;{ prepare, layout }&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">from</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">'@chenglou/pretext'</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">const</span>&nbsp;prepared =&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__title\">prepare</span>(<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">'AGI 春天到了. بدأت الرحلة 🚀'</span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">'16px Inter'</span>)</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">const</span>&nbsp;{ height, lineCount } =&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__title\">layout</span>(prepared, textWidth,&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">20</span>)</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">// height 就是精确的像素高度，全程没碰 DOM</span></span></code><br></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">高级用法：手动逐行布局</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"javascript\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">import</span>&nbsp;{ prepareWithSegments, layoutWithLines }&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">from</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">'@chenglou/pretext'</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">const</span>&nbsp;prepared =&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__title\">prepareWithSegments</span>(<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">'一些文本'</span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">'18px \"Helvetica Neue\"'</span>)</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">const</span>&nbsp;{ lines } =&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__title\">layoutWithLines</span>(prepared,&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">320</span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">26</span>)</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">for</span>&nbsp;(<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">let</span>&nbsp;i =&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">0</span>; i &lt; lines.<span class=\"code-snippet__property\">length</span>; i++) {</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; ctx.<span class=\"code-snippet__title\">fillText</span>(lines[i].<span class=\"code-snippet__property\">text</span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">0</span>, i *&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">26</span>)</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">}</span></code><br></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">本地跑 Demo</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"bash\"><code><span leaf=\"\">git&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">clone</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/chenglou/pretext.git\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/chenglou/pretext.git</a></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">cd</span>&nbsp;pretext</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">bun install</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">bun start</span></code><br></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">然后浏览器打开 <a href=\"http://127.0.0.1:3000/demos\" target=\"_blank\">http://127.0.0.1:3000/demos</a> 就能看到了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">这个不碰 DOM 就能预测文本高度的能力。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">虚拟滚动、瀑布流、聊天 UI，这些天天在用的东西，以前要么牺牲性能去量，要么用估算值凑合。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 16px;line-height: 2em;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">现在有个 15KB、零依赖、100% 准确率的方案摆在这里，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">拿来就能用。</span></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "介绍开源项目 Pretext，一个高性能、零依赖的 JavaScript 文本测量与布局库，通过两阶段架构解决了传统 DOM 测量带来的性能瓶颈。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "介绍开源项目 Pretext，一个高性能、零依赖的 JavaScript 文本测量与布局库，通过两阶段架构解决了传统 DOM 测量带来的性能瓶颈。",
  "summary": "Pretext 是一个由前 React 核心开发者推出的开源库，旨在解决 Web 开发中长期存在的文本测量性能问题。它通过将文本测量拆分为“准备”和“布局”两个阶段，避免了频繁操作 DOM 导致的重排（Layout Thrashing），在虚拟滚动、聊天界面等场景中性能提升显著。该项目不仅支持多语言，还展示了 AI 辅助开发的成功实践，是前端性能优化领域的一个重要工具。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "解决传统 DOM 测量导致的性能瓶颈。",
      "explanation": "传统测量方法（如 getBoundingClientRect）会触发浏览器强制重排，Pretext 通过纯算术运算实现测量，性能提升 200 倍以上，特别适合虚拟滚动和瀑布流场景。"
    },
    {
      "point": "创新的两阶段架构设计。",
      "explanation": "将测量拆分为 prepare（缓存计算）和 layout（轻量级算术）两步，窗口变化时仅需极速重算，极大优化了响应式布局性能。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 辅助开发的标杆案例。",
      "explanation": "作者在开发过程中利用 AI 进行跨浏览器渲染对比测试，确保了在不同环境下 100% 的准确率，为 AI 编程提供了优秀范例。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "在不碰 DOM 的情况下，精确算出一段文字在给定宽度下会有多高。",
    "Pretext 把文本测量拆成了两步：第一步是 prepare，负责分词、处理双向文本、用 Canvas measureText 测量；第二步是 layout，基于缓存的宽度做纯算术运算。",
    "这是一个 AI 辅助开发的标杆案例。开发者 Cheng Lou 在开发过程中大量使用了 Claude Code 和 Codex，让 AI 在几十种容器宽度下对比浏览器的真实渲染结果。"
  ],
